text: The Plandemic: Indoctornation video premiered on Aug. 18 as a sequel to the coronavirus conspiracy theory-laden Plandemic video that went viral in May. Like its predecessor, the sequel makes misleading and false claims about a variety of topics related to the COVID-19 pandemic.
